description.content:
I will do WordPress Responsive Website Development or Fix WordPress Issues


I am a seasoned WordPress expert with over 8 years of experience crafting exceptional websites for businesses and individuals worldwide. I specialize in delivering high-performance, SEO-optimized websites that leave a lasting impression.


My Services:


1. WordPress Website Development:


  • WP Installation
  • Premium Theme Installations
  • Blogs Web Development
  • E-Commerce Web Development
  • Custom Website from Scratch using Elementor Pro
  • Custom Design with WP Bakery
  • Design with Your theme builder
  • Landing Page Creation
  • Social Media Integration
  • Contact Forms
  • WooCommerce with payment gateway set-up
  • Custom Woocommerce Product/ Shop Pages using Elementor Pro


 

2. Plugin Installation & Configuration


  • Premium or free


3. WordPress Modification


  • Fix WP basic issues
  • Theme Modification
  • Design Modification
  • SSL Installation on WordPress
  • WP Redirection issues
  • Form Creations
  • HTACCES issues
  • WordPress Migration


Note: Please Dont place order Directly, Discuss with me then place order

reviews.comment: Excellent....starting a new blog. He helped me transfer my blog/domain and blog posts off a hosting platform. Rebuilt it on Wordpress . Walked me through and patiently taught me the steps. As well as zoom calls and the proper documentation. This is my second or third project with him. As well as I have some future projects as well.

Again, its been a pleasure working with someone who really knows and understand not only my needs but the guidance. He even went above and beyond and jumped on a zoom call. Professionalism and efficient. I'm glad to be working with him again and am already going to book him for my third order.

Omg! He is an absolute gem of a human! He spent 3 hours with me helping me learn how to navigate my new website. I met him trying to optimize my Adsense because it was so annoying, but he talked me into fixing my page, and boy did he deliver!!! He made it really professional and fast and optimized my pages and then spent time helping me learn. Absolutely amazing to work with! Will hire him again for seo when i bring my dA up!
Definitely the ALL Around Website Guru! USE HIM ONLY
He did an amazing job. Quick and brought the vision to life. Will definitely use him again
